ball club season \n|club = [[Bologna F.C. 1909|Bologna Associazione Giuoco del Calcio]]\n|season = 1938-39\n|manager = [[\u00c1rp\u00e1d Weisz]], (until 26 October 1938)<br />[[Hermann Felsner]]\n|chairman = [[Renato Dall'Ara]]\n|chrtitle= President\n|league = [[Serie A]]\n|league result = [[1938-39 Serie A|1\u00ba]] (in [[1939 Mitropa Cup]] )\n|cup1 = [[Coppa Italia]]\n|cup1 result = [[1938-39 Coppa Italia|round of 32]]\n|cup2 = [[Mitropa Cup]]\n|cup2 result = [[1939 Mitropa Cup|Semifinals]]\n|league topscorer = [[Ettore Puricelli|Puricelli]] (19)\n|season topscorer = Puricelli (23)\n\n|pattern_la1 = _redlower\n|leftarm1 = 000066\n|pattern_b1 = _3navystripes\n|body1 = FF0000\n|pattern_ra1 = _redlower\n|rightarm1 = 000066\n|shorts1 = FFFFFF\n|socks1 = 000066\n\n|prevseason = [[1937-38 Bologna season|1937-38]]\n|nextseason = [[1939-40 Bologna season|1939-40]]\n}}\n\nDuring the 1938-39 season '''Bologna Associazione Giuoco del Calcio''' competed in Serie A, Coppa Italia and Central European Cup.\n\n== Summary ==\nThe club won its 5th league championship ever <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bibliotecasalaborsa.it/cronologia/bologna/1939/quinto_scudetto_del_bologna_fc|title=quinto scudetto del Bologna|publisher=biblioteca salaborsa}}</ref>, winning the race against [[Torino F. C.|Torino]]. Weisz was replaced by German Felsner on round 6<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dlib.coninet.it/bookreader.php?&f=3365&p=1&c=1#page/4/mode/2up|title=Felsner sostituisce Veisz come istruttore del Bologna a partire da oggi|publisher=Il Littoriale, n. 267|date=27 October 1938|p=4}}</ref> The squad, after a 4-0 score against [[S.S.C. Napoli|Napoli]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dlib.coninet.it/bookreader.php?&c=1&f=3639&p=6#page/6/mode/2up|title=Echi del clamoroso insuccesso del Napoli|publisher=Il Littoriale, n. 14|date=17 January 1939|p=6}}</ref><ref name=Improta>Mario Improta, Numeri Azzurri, Fratelli Frilli Editori, pagine 48 e 50</ref><ref>[http://www.napolissimo.net/Torneo%201938-1939.html Napolissimo.net - Torneo 1938/1939]</ref> on 21 May 1939, clinched the title <ref>{{cite web|url=http://badigit.comune.bologna.it/mostre/bologna_fc/unsecolodiallenatori.htm|publisher=badigit comune bologna|title=quattro matti dietro una palla}}</ref>.\n\n== Squad ==\n{{fs start}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Carlo Ceresoli]]|pos=GK}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Pietro Ferrari]]|pos=GK}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Dino Fiorini]]|pos=DF}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Mario Montesanto]]|pos=DF}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Mario Pagotto]]|pos=DF}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Secondo Ricci]]|pos=DF}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Aldo Tugnoli]]|pos=DF}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Michele Andreolo]]|pos=MF}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Giordano Corsi]]|pos=MF}}\n{{fs mid}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Francisco Fedullo]]|pos=MF}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Aurelio Marchese]]|pos=MF}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Raffaele Sansone]]|pos=MF}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Piero Andreoli]]|pos=FW}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Amedeo Biavati]]|pos=FW}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Bruno Maini]]|pos=FW}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=URU|name=[[Ettore Puricelli]]|pos=MF}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Carlo Reguzzoni]]|pos=FW}}\n{{fs player|no=|nat=ITA|name=[[Alcide Ivan Violi]]|pos=FW}}\n{{fs end}}\n\n== Competitions ==\n=== Serie A ===\n{{main|1938-39 Serie A }}\n====League table====\n{{:1938-39 Serie A|showteam=BOL}}\n==== Matches ====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 18 September 1938\n|round = 1\n|team1 = [[Genoa Cricket and Football Club|Genoa 1938]]\n|team2 = Bologna\n|score = 2-3\n|report=\n|location = [[Genova]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Luigi Ferraris]]\n|attendance = 14 000\n|referee = Giacomo Bertolio\n|goals1 = [[Luigi Scarabello|Scarabello]] {{Goal|8}}<br />[[Angelo Cattaneo|Cattaneo]] {{Goal|81}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|39}} [[Mario Montesanto|Montesanto]]<br />{{Goal|59}} [[Amedeo Biavati|Biavati]]<br />{{Goal|77}} [[Ettore