llini]] {{Goal|50}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|37}} [[Ettore Puricelli|Puricelli]]\n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 21 April 1939\n|round = 27\n|team1 = Bologna\n|team2 = Modena\n|score = 1-1\n|report=\n|location = [[Bologna]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Renato Dall'Ara|Stadio Littoriale]]\n|attendance = 10 000\n|referee = Attilio Soliani\n|goals1 = [[Raffaele Sansone|Sansone]] {{Goal|77}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|25}} [[Vittorio Sentimenti|Sentimenti III]]\n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 30 April 1939\n|round= 28\n|team1 = [[A.S. Roma|Roma]]\n|team2 = Bologna\n|score = 0-1\n|report=\n|location= [[Rome|Roma]]\n|stadium  = [[Campo Testaccio]]\n|attendance = 12 000\n|referee = Rinaldo Barlassina\n|goals1=\n|goals2 = {{Goal|47}} [[Ettore Puricelli|Puricelli]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 21 May 1939\n|round = 29\n|team1 = Bologna\n|team2 = [[S.S.C. Napoli|Napoli]]\n|score = 4-0\n|report=\n|location = [[Bologna]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Renato Dall'Ara|Stadio Littoriale]]\n|attendance = 6 000\n|referee = Giovanni Galeati\n|goals1 = [[Michele Andreolo|Andreolo]] {{Goal|5}}<br />[[Carlo Reguzzoni|Reguzzoni]] {{Goal|67}}<br />[[Luigi Castello|Castello]] {{Goal|77|aut.}}<br />[[Ettore Puricelli|Puricelli]] {{Goal|85}}\n|goals2=\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 28 May 1939\n|round = 30\n|team1 = [[Inter Milan|Ambrosiana-Inter]]\n|team2 = Bologna\n|score = 2-0\n|report=\n|location = [[Milano]]\n|stadium  = [[Arena Civica]]\n|referee = Generoso Dattilo\n|goals1 = [[Enrico Candiani|Candiani]] {{Goal|38}}<br />[[Umberto Guarnieri|Guarnieri]] {{Goal|64}}\n|result=L\n}}\n\n=== Coppa Italia ===\n{{main|1938\u201339 Coppa Italia}}\n==== Round of 32 ====\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 25 December 1938\n|team1 = Triestina\n|team2 = Bologna\n|score = 1-0\n|report=\n|location = [[Trieste]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Giuseppe Grezar|Stadio Littorio]]\n|attendance = 3 000\n|referee = Giovanni Tonnetti\n|goals1 = [[Gino Colaussi|Colaussi]] 