g.com/fighter/Ben-Askren-42390|title=Ben|last=Sherdog.com|website=Sherdog|access-date=2019-10-26}}</ref>\n\n==Freestyle record==\n{{s-start}}\n|-\n!  Res.\n!  Record\n!  Opponent\n!  Score\n!  Date\n!  Event\n!  Location\n|-\n! style=background:white colspan=7 |{{small|2008 [[Wrestling at the 2008 Summer Olympics|Olympic]] 6th at 74kg}}\n|-\n| {{no2}}Loss\n| 5-1\n| align=left | {{flagicon|CUB}} [[Ivan Fundora]]\n| style=\"font-size:88%\"|1\u20133, 0\u20134\n| style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=2|August 12, 2008\n| style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=2|[[2008 Olympic Games]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;font-size:88%;\" rowspan=2|{{flagicon|CHN}} [[Beijing]], [[China]]\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| 5-0\n| align=left | {{flagicon|HUN}} [[Istv\u00e1n Ver\u00e9b]]\n| style=\"font-size:88%\"|Fall\n|-\n! style=background:white colspan=7 |{{small| 2008 US World Team Trials {{gold1}} at 74kg}}\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| 4-0\n| align=left | {{flagicon|USA}} Tyrone Lewis\n| style=\"font-size:88%\"|2-0, 1-0\n| style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=4|June 15, 2008\n| style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=4| 2008 US World Team Trials\n| style=\"text-align:left;font-size:88%;\" rowspan=4|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Las Vegas]], [[Nevada]], United States\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| 3-0\n| align=left | {{flagicon|USA}} Tyrone Lewis\n| style=\"font-size:88%\"|2-6, 2-0, 1-0\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| 2-0\n| align=left | {{flagicon|USA}} Ramico Blackmon\n| style=\"font-size:88%\"|1-0, 2-1\n|-\n| {{yes2}}Win\n| 1\u20130\n| align=left | {{flagicon|USA}} [[Donny Pritzlaff]]\n| style=\"font-size:88%\"|3-0, 1-1\n|-\n{{end}}\n\n==NCAA Record==\n{{s-start}}\n! colspan=\"8\"| NCAA Championships Matches\n|-\n!  Res.\n!  Record\n!  Opponent\n!  Score\n!  Date\n!  Event\n|-\n! style=background:white colspan=6 |2007 [[NCAA Division I Wrestling Championships|NCAA Championships]] {{gold1}} at 174&nbsp;lbs\n|-\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|17-2\n|align=left|Keith Gavin\n|style=\"font-size:88%\"|8-2\n|style=\"font-size:88%\" rowspan=5|March 17, 2007\n|style=\"font-si