ilippe, who was said to have been inspired by American school shootings and had planned the attack for several months, wanted to take revenge on 7\u20138 of his schoolmates with whom he didn't get along.<ref>[http://www.lepoint.fr/actualites-societe/2008-05-01/le-collegien-qui-a-poignarde-3-camarades-a-meyzieu-mis-en-examen/920/0/241916 Le coll\u00e9gien qui a poignard\u00e9 3 camarades \u00e0 Meyzieu mis en examen], ''[[Le Point]]'' (April 29, 2008)</ref><ref>[http://www.francesoir.fr/faits-divers/2008/05/02/violence-a-l-ecole-le-souffre-douleur-devenu-bourreau.html Violence \u00e0 l'\u00e9cole \u2013 Le souffre-douleur devenu bourreau Apr\u00e8s la folie meurtri\u00e8re du coll\u00e9gien] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210173304/http://www.francesoir.fr/faits-divers/2008/05/02/violence-a-l-ecole-le-souffre-douleur-devenu-bourreau.html |date=2008-12-10 }}, ''[[France-Soir]]'' (May 2, 2008)</ref><ref>[http://tempsreel.nouvelobs.com/actualites/societe/20080430.OBS2153/mise_en_examen_du_collegien_qui_a_poignarde_3_camarades.html Mise en examen du coll\u00e9gien qui a poignard\u00e9 3 camarades pr\u00e8s de Lyon], ''[[Le Nouvel Observateur]]'' (June 23, 2008)</ref>\n|-\n| May 12, 2008\n| [[Cornwall, Ontario]], Canada\n| ..., 17\n| 1 dead\n|\n| A 16-year-old boy was stabbed to death in a classroom at the T.R. Leger School by a 17-year-old classmate shortly before noon. The suspect fled the scene along a nearby bicycle path, but following a brief foot chase, was apprehended without incident. It was later revealed that the two individuals were involved in a fight outside the school earlier that morning, and the suspect went home to get a knife before returning to school.<ref>{{cite web |last=Ottawa |first=The |url=http://www.canada.com/ottawacitizen/news/city/story.html?id=6f768976-5f85-40d6-ad0e-4375c571ace9 |title=Boy, 16, dies in classroom stabbing 17-year-old faces first-degree murder charges in Cornwall |publisher=Canada.com |date=2008-05-13 |acces