isi, dolore e rabbia Fischi ai politici: \"Ora ammazzateci tutti\" - Bari - Repubblica.it|website=Bari - La Repubblica}}</ref>\n|-\n| May 25, 2012\n| [[Sankt Poelten]], [[Austria]]\n| Unidentified male, 37\n| 1 dead \n| 1 injured\n| Shortly after 8:00 local time, an armed 37-year-old man broke into Volksschule Wagram in Sankt Poelten, [[Austria]] and hauled his two children out of the classroom. His daughter managed to escape, which promoted him to take his 8-year-old son to a cloakroom and shot him in the head, critically injuring him. The father then escaped from the school in a car, and later committed suicide after he crashed his car on a local farm road. The most likely motive of his actions is that he wanted to get revenge on his wife.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://diepresse.com/home/panorama/oesterreich/761026/Schule_Vater-schiesst-Sohn-in-den-Kopf|title=Schule: Vater schie\u00dft Sohn in den Kopf|website=diepresse.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| August 16, 2012\n| [[Memphis, Tennessee]], United States\n| \n|\n| 2 injured\n| Two Hamilton High School students were shot and wounded in the parking lot of the school. The attack was believed to be gang-related.<ref>{{cite news|last=Carroll |first=Scott|url=http://www.commercialappeal.com/news/2012/aug/16/crime-report-woman-shot-in-argument-over-5-loan/?partner=RSS |title=CRIME REPORT: Students involved in gang-related shooting outside Hamilton High School |newspaper=Commercial Appeal |date=August 16, 2012 |accessdate=January 15, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|August 27, 2012}}\n|{{sort|Perry Hall, Maryland}}, United States\n|Robert Wayne Gladden, Jr., 15\n|<span style=\"display:none\">0,000,001</span>\n|<span style=\"display:none\">0,000,001</span>1 injured\n| Robert Gladden, 15, took a [[double barrel shotgun]] to [[Perry Hall High School]] and fired shots inside the school cafeteria. A 17-year-old senior with [[Down syndrome]] was hit in the lower back while he was sitting at a table and suffered critical wounds. Gladden was immediat