ombres-de-heridos-por-disparos-en-colegio-americano| title=Spread of names of gunshot wounded at American College (Spanish)|work=[[SDP Noticias]]| date=18 January 2017| author=}}</ref> Guevara had psychological problems.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2017/01/18/gunfire-erupts-at-mexican-private-school-injuries-reported.html| title=15-year-old student shoots teacher, 3 classmates at American school in Mexico|work=[[Fox News]] (World)| date=2 March 2016| author=}}</ref> Teacher Cecilia Cristina Solis died on March 29, 2017, hours after being declared brain dead.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.milenio.com/region/muere-maestra-baleada-colegio_americano_noreste-milenio-monterrey_0_928707377.html| title=Muere Maestra baleada en Colegio Americano del Noreste (Spanish)|work=[[Milenio]]| date=29 March 2017| author=}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|January 20, 2017}}\n|[[West Liberty, Ohio]], US \n| Student, 17\n|\n| 1 injured\n| A student was shot and injured by another student at [[West Liberty-Salem High School]].\n|-\n|{{Dts|March 16, 2017}}\n|[[Grasse, France]] \n| Kylian Barbey, 17 (charged)\n|\n| 4 injured\n| Kylian Barbey, a 17-year-old boy, armed with a [[rifle]], two [[handguns]], a [[revolver]] and two [[grenades]], opened fire at Alexis de Tocqueville high school. A total of four were injured, three students and the school's principal. Anti-terrorist commandos were sent to the scene and the shooter was arrested. The perpetrator's [[Facebook]] and [[YouTube]] accounts showed that he was interested in the [[Columbine Massacre]] and watched videos on how to make homemade weapons.<ref>{{cite web|author=<!--Not stated-->|title=Teenager held over French school shooting|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-39292755|website=BBC News|date=16 March 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|May 15, 2017}}\n|Guachipelin de Escazu, [[Costa Rica]]\n| Unknown group of assailants in van\n| 2 dead\n| 1 injured\n| A group of men in a van attempted to assassinate a Lebanese man while he