ring. He later stated when the moment came, and he saw a female students distress in reaction to seeing him, he couldn't bring himself to hurt anyone. Instead he fired a shot at a nearby closed door, without aiming. He later claimed that he \"didn't think the gun would fire\". A 17-year-old male student in the classroom was wounded after he was shot in the ankle. Bouche then entered the classroom of one of his former teachers, and surrendered peacefully to the responding SRO. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ocala.com/news/20190420/one-year-after-shooting-at-ocalas-forest-high-school|title=One year after the shooting at Ocala\u2019s Forest High School |date=April 20, 2019 |work=OcalaStarBanner}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|April 27, 2018}}\n|[[Shaanxi]], China\n| Zhao, 28\n| 9 dead\n| 10 injured\n| Nine students were stabbed to death and 10 injured in a knife attack outside a school in northern China. The man who carried out the attack was reportedly a former student, taking revenge for having been bullied at the school. The dead were seven girls and two boys aged 12 to 15.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-43921567|title=China stabbings: Nine students killed in Shaanxi |date=April 28, 2018 |work=BBC News}}</ref>\n|-\n|May 25, 2018\n|[[Palmdale, California]], US\n| -\n| -\n|1 injured\n|A 14 year old male opened fire with a rifle at roughly 7:00&nbsp;a.m. at [[Highland High School (Palmdale, California)|Highland High School]] campus and then walked into a bathroom, The shots wounded one former schoolmate, a male who was shot in his arm. The suspect shot 10 rounds. He then dumped the gun in a field before he was taken into custody in a nearby shopping center.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dailynews.com/2018/05/11/deputies-respond-to-report-of-man-with-a-gun-at-palmdales-highland-high-school//|title= Student shot at Highland High School in Palmdale, former schoolmate in custody |last=|first=|date=2018-05-18|work=CBS Interactive Inc.|access-date=2018-0