 man fatally shot at Tenn. high school |publisher=NBC News |date=2010-08-30 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| September 8, 2010\n| [[Detroit]], [[Michigan]], United States\n| Steven Jamal Hare, 17\n|\n| 2 injured\n| Two students were shot and wounded in front of [[Mumford High School]]. A 17-year-old, Steven Jamal Hare, was tried as an adult and charged with assault with intent to kill. In 2012, Hare was sentenced to 27 years of prison.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://statecasefiles.justia.com/documents/michigan/court-of-appeals-unpublished/305104.pdf?ts=1348661231 |title=PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN VS. STEVEN JAMAL HARE |publisher=State of Michigan |accessdate=September 5, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| October 1, 2010\n| [[Salinas, California|Salinas]],<br>[[California]],<br>United States\n|\n| 1 dead\n|\n| 15-year-old student Jose Cisneros was shot to death on an athletic field at [[Alisal High School]], as he was walking to school. Police said that the shooting was gang-related.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kionrightnow.com/Global/story.asp?S=13251739 |title=Student Dies From Gun Shots at Alisal High School |publisher=Kionrightnow.com |accessdate=2011-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111128161341/http://www.kionrightnow.com/Global/story.asp?S=13251739 |archive-date=2011-11-28 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| October 10, 2010\n| [[Santa Clarita, California|Santa Clarita]],<br>[[California]],<br>United States\n|\n|\n| 2 injured\n| A 16-year-old girl at [[William S. Hart High School]] was stabbed on campus with a kitchen knife, during a lunchtime fight over a boy with another female student. The victim was taken to [[Henry Mayo Newhall Memorial Hospital]] with a stab wound to the chest. The girl believed to have done the stabbing was also hospitalized with unspecified injuries.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2010/10/16-year-old-hart-high-student-stabbed-during-lunchtime-fight-on-newhall-campus.html |title=High school student in Ne