ents distress in reaction to seeing him, he couldn't bring himself to hurt anyone. Instead he fired a shot at a nearby closed door, without aiming. He later claimed that he \"didn't think the gun would fire\". A 17-year-old male student in the classroom was wounded after he was shot in the ankle. Bouche then entered the classroom of one of his former teachers, and surrendered peacefully to the responding SRO. <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ocala.com/news/20190420/one-year-after-shooting-at-ocalas-forest-high-school|title=One year after the shooting at Ocala\u2019s Forest High School |date=April 20, 2019 |work=OcalaStarBanner}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{Dts|April 27, 2018}}\n|[[Shaanxi]], China\n| Zhao, 28\n| 9 dead\n| 10 injured\n| Nine students were stabbed to death and 10 injured in a knife attack outside a school in northern China. The man who carried out the attack was reportedly a former student, taking revenge for having been bullied at the school. The dead were seven girls and two boys aged 12 to 15.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-43921567|title=China stabbings: Nine students killed in Shaanxi |date=April 28, 2018 |work=BBC News}}</ref>\n|-\n|May 25, 2018\n|[[Palmdale, California]], US\n| -\n| -\n|1 injured\n|A 14 year old male opened fire with a rifle at roughly 7:00&nbsp;a.m. at [[Highland High School (Palmdale, California)|Highland High School]] campus and then walked into a bathroom, The shots wounded one former schoolmate, a male who was shot in his arm. The suspect shot 10 rounds. He then dumped the gun in a field before he was taken into custody in a nearby shopping center.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dailynews.com/2018/05/11/deputies-respond-to-report-of-man-with-a-gun-at-palmdales-highland-high-school//|title= Student shot at Highland High School in Palmdale, former schoolmate in custody |last=|first=|date=2018-05-18|work=CBS Interactive Inc.|access-date=2018-05-19|language=en-US}}</ref>\n|-\n|May 18, 2018\n|[[Santa Fe, Texas]], US\n|Dimitrios Pagourtzis, 17\n|10 dead\n|14 injured\n|[[Santa Fe High School shooting]]. A student armed with a shotgun and a .38 revolver smuggled under his coat opened fire on [[Santa Fe High School (Texas)|Santa Fe High School]] campus, killing 10 people, many of them his fellow students, and wounding 10 more.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/05/18/us/school-shooting-santa-fe-texas.html|title=Texas School Shooting: 10 Dead, 10 Hurt, and Many Not Surprised It Happened|last=Fernandez|first=Manny|date=2018-05-18|work=The New York Times|access-date=2018-05-19|last2=Fausset|first2=Richard|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|last3=Bidgood|first3=Jess}}</ref>\n|-\n|May 25, 2018\n|[[Noblesville, Indiana]], US\n| Student, 13\n| -\n|2 injured\n|[[Noblesville West Middle School shooting]]. A student opened fire at 9:06.<ref name=\"f59-what-we-know\">{{cite news|title=Here\u2019s what we know about the Noblesville West Middle School shooting that injured student, teacher|url=http://fox59.com/2018/05/25/heres-what-we-know-about-the-noblesville-west-middle-school-shooting/|accessdate=25 May 2018|agency=FOX59}}</ref> a.m. on [[Noblesville West Middle School]] campus, injuring two; an adult and a teenager. After the incident, the suspect came into custody.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/indiana-school-shooting-report-of-shots-fired-at-noblesville-west-middle-school/|title=Police: 2 injured in shooting at Noblesville West Middle School in Indiana|last=|first=|date=2018-05-18|work=CBS Interactive Inc.|access-date=2018-05-19|language=en-US}}</ref>\n|-\n|October 17, 2018\n|[[Kerch]]\n| Vladislav Roslyakov, 18\n|21 dead\n|70 injured\n|The [[Kerch Polytechnic College massacre]]. An 18-year-old student at the [[Kerch Polytechnic College]] set off explosives in the school and began shooting, killing 20. The shooter was highly inspired by the [[Columbine High School Massacre]], even going as far as wearing the same clothes as one of the two shooters involved in that attack.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-45891201|title=Gun attack at Crimea college kills 19|date=October 17, 2018|via=www.bbc.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|December 17, 2018\n|[[Haridwar, Uttarakhand]], India\n| Student, 13\n| -\n|1 injured\n| DAV Public School shooting in Haridwar\n|-\n|February 11, 2019\n|[[Stowbtsy]], Belarus\n| Student, 15\n| 2 dead\n| 2 injured\n| A 15-year-old student stabbed a 50-year-old history teacher in the neck, who then died on the spot. He also stabbed two students, who tried to defend the teacher, injuring both of them. The assailant then left the class and entered a nearby classroom, where he stabbed a 17-year-old student, who also died on the spot.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/belarusian-teen-suspected-of-stabbing-teacher-classmate-to-death/29763228.html|title=Belarusian Teen Suspected Of Stabbing Teacher, Classmate To Death |date=February 11, 2019 |work=RadioFreeEurope/RadioLiberty}}</ref>\n|-\n|February 26, 2019\n|[[Toronto]], Ontario\n| Unknown\n| \n| 2 injured\n| A fight between two students ended off with a double stabbing.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://toronto.citynews.ca/2019/02/26/stabbing-york-memorial-collegiate/|title=2 students stabbed outside York Memorial Collegiate Institute |date=February 26, 2019 |work=CityNews}}</ref>\n|-\n|March 13, 2019\n|[[Suzano]], Brazil\n| Guilherme Taucci Monteiro, 17; Luiz Henrique de Castro, 25\n| 10 dead\n| 11 injured\n| [[Suzano massacre|Two masked]] men shot and killed 6 students and 2 staff members at a public secondary school in Suzano, Brazil. Eleven additional victims were wounded. The suspects committed suicide inside the school.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/2019/03/13/americas/brazil-school-shooting/index.html/|title=At least 8 people were killed in a school shooting in Brazil |date=March 13, 2019 |work=CNN}}</ref>\n|-\n| May 7, 2019\n| Colorado, United States\n| Devon Erickson, 18; Maya Elizabeth, 16\n| 1 dead\n| 8 injured\n| At the [[